* Iron Raptor hadn't heard Prowl come up to her but had gasped in surprise as she was then lifted into his arms, her optics suddenly wide but then look tired again in moments as she then relaxed.
With a sigh she closed her optics and then relaxed fully in Prowl's arms, letting her head lean against his chest after she had felt him kiss her.
Her side hurt like it had never hurt before but she was much to tired to care at this point, consciousness soon beginning to slip away from her as her breathing soon began to even out and become more softer.
It wasn't long until the only bot in which Prowl held was nothing more then a sleeping bot, all worries and pains forgotten as the world or reality had slipped away to nothing more then a mere murmur.*
